ruby-odbc-0.4

This is an ODBC binding for Ruby. So far it has been tested with

    - Ruby 1.6.3, MySQL 3.22, unixODBC 2.0.6
      on Linux 2.2-x86

    - Ruby 1.6.3, MySQL 3.22/MyODBC (remote), MS Jet Engine, MSVC++ 6.0
      on Windows NT4SP6

    Michael Neumann <neumann@s-direktnet.de> reported successful compilation
    with Cygwin on Win32.

Requirements:

    - Ruby 1.6.3
    - unixODBC 2.0.x on UN*X

Installation:

    $ ruby extconf.rb
    $ make
    # make install

Testing:

    $ ruby test.rb DSN [uid] [pwd]

Usage:

    Refer to doc/odbc.html

